headline: GE Aerospace Bets On Singapore AI Repair Hub And Services Growth
summary: GE Aerospace, part of General Electric (NYSE:GE), is committing a major multi year investment to expand its engine repair capabilities in Singapore. The plan includes advanced automation, AI enabled inspection technologies, and a formal partnership with Singapore's Economic Development Board. The expansion targets growing demand for aircraft engine maintenance and services across the Asia Pacific aviation market.
